### Response
### Status Code: 404
### Body: {"Error": "Not found"}
PUT  http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{NON_EXISTENT_EXERCISE_ID}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Deadlift",
    "reps": 12,
    "weight": 30,
    "unit": "lbs",
    "date": "06-25-24"
}


### Request 19: Delete the Deadlift with date 07-18-24
### Response
### Status Code: 204 status code
### Body: empty
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{DEADLIFT_ID}} HTTP/1.1


### Request 20: Verify that the exercise has been deleted
### Response
### Status Code: 200
### Body: An array. The array must contain the 3 exercises created by requests 2, 3 and 4.
###     It must not contain the exercise created by request 1 (Deadlift with date 07-18-24)
GET http://localhost:3000/exercises HTTP/1.1


### Request 21: Delete exercise just deleted
### Response
### Status Code: 404 status code
### Body: {"Error": "Not found"}
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{DEADLIFT_ID}} HTTP/1.1


### Request 22: Delete exercise with non-existent ID
### Response
### Status Code: 404 status code
### Body: {"Error": "Not found"}
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{NON_EXISTENT_EXERCISE_ID}} HTTP/1.1
